d-Explorer-Transmission-Repair-Charlotte-NC" data-counter="right"></script>&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>
<!-- Place this tag where you want the su badge to render -->
<div style='float: left;clear: right; padding-right: 4px; margin-top: 5px; display: block; bottom: 0; left: 0; height: 60px;'><su:badge layout="1" location="http://www.twincharlotte.com/transmission-repair-blog/bid/34825/2003-Ford-Explorer-Transmission-Repair-Charlotte-NC"></su:badge></div><div class= 'smallsocial' style='float:left; clear:right; font-size:medium; margin-top:2px; display:block; height:26px;'><a href='http://www.twincharlotte.com/CMS/UI/Modules/BizBlogger/LinkSubmission.aspx?bid=34825&pid=12698&tid=157987&mid=217365&srv=delicious&trk=0' 
