	<h3 class="title"><a href="http://www.twincharlotte.com/transmission-repair-blog/bid/26057/2003-Ford-Windstar-Transmission-Repair-Charlotte-NC" title="2003 Ford Windstar Transmission Repair | Charlotte NC">2003 Ford Windstar Transmission Repair | Charlotte NC</a></h3>
	<div class="byline">
		Posted by Beth Jackson on Tue, Feb 15, 2011 @ 09:03 AM
	</div>
	<div class="submissions">
		<div style='clear: right;
