	<h3 class="title"><a href="http://www.twincharlotte.com/transmission-repair-blog/bid/19717/2002-Ford-Explorer-Transmission-Repair-Charlotte-NC" title="2002 Ford Explorer Transmission Repair | Charlotte NC">2002 Ford Explorer Transmission Repair | Charlotte NC</a></h3>
